<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="description"
        content="Gerador automático de dashboard com conteúdo educacional visando à modernização das técnicas de ensino">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script type="application/javascript" src="/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/imgs/favicon/favicon.ico">
    <style>
        .form-control,
        .form-label,
        .form-select,
        .btn,
        .card-title,
        .form-text {
            font-size: 18pt;
        }

        .card-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .card-body {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
    <title>DashGen - Esqueci minha senha</title>
</head>

<body class="container bg-light fs-4">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light mb-4">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <img src="/imgs/dashGenLogo.png" alt="" width="60" height="44">
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
                aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" aria-current="page" href="/register">Fazer cadastro</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" aria-current="page" href="/">Entrar</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <%- include('../partials/flash'); -%>

    <h1 class="mb-4">Mudar senha</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">Insira seu email no campo abaixo e, se o mesmo constar em nosso banco de dados, iremos te enviar um
        email com as instruções para mudar sua senha.</p>
    <form class="mb-4" action="/forgotPwd" method="POST">
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="email" class="form-label">Insira seu email</label>
            <input type="email" class="form-control fs-4" id="email" name="email">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary fs-4">Enviar email</button>
    </form>
</body>

</html>